summary: This is an email chain from November 10, 2009, discussing the storage location of boxes related to the Epstein case, specifically whether they contain grand jury materials or case files and whether they should be moved to a locked grand jury room on the 4th floor.
keyFacts: Email correspondence dated November 10, 2009, discusses storage of Epstein-related materials.
References boxes on the 9th floor and questions whether they contain grand jury materials or just case files.
Suggests moving materials to a locked grand jury room on the 4th floor, where they were previously stored.
Indicates an ongoing need to manage and secure case documents related to Epstein.
